<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent0a55b6522113449f9f3eb09e920bf8c0">
</div>
<p>At The Royal Marsden we have access to a wide pool of high-quality expertise to consult or involve in your cancer care. We are also able to link with services closer to your home.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="panel staff-details">
<div class="staff-title pad">
<div id="imageContentf1622db249c94bd5b5713bfd30f029b5">
</div>
<h3 id="member53">Carla Reid</h3>
<p><em>Adolescent and Young People Physiotherapist</em></p>
<p>Carla Reid qualified as a physiotherapist in 2005. After working as a senior paediatric physiotherapist, Carla joined the physiotherapy team at The Royal Marsden in 2009. Carla’s main aim is to develop an excellent and efficient service where young people can minimise the physical impact of cancer and its treatment, and promote independence and hence an enhanced quality of life.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:carla.reid@rmh.nhs.uk">carla.reid@rmh.nhs.uk</a></p>
</div>
<div class="staff-info pad">
<h4>Qualifications</h4>
<p>BSc (Hons) Physiotherapy</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="panel staff-details">
