</div>
<h3 id="member52">Louise Soanes</h3>
<p><em>TCT Nurse Consultant for Adolescents and Young Adults</em></p>
<p>Louise has worked at The Royal Marsden since 2002, and has been nurse  consultant for adolescents and young adults since 2008. She works with  teams across the trust and partner hospitals to establish TYA care  cancer.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:lsoanes@nhs.net">lsoanes@nhs.net</a></p>
</div>
<div class="staff-info pad">
<h4>Qualifications</h4>
<p>RSCN/RGN</p>
